Privacy Policy
"Zen Ring · Nine Linked Rings" Application
Last Updated: July 26, 2024
This Privacy Policy informs you about how we collect, use, and protect your information when you use the "Zen Ring · Nine Linked Rings" mobile application (hereinafter referred to as "the App").
1. Information Collection and Use
The App does not collect any personally identifiable information.
•
Non-Personal Information: The App may store game progress-related data locally on your device, such as your current level, steps taken, and the state of the nine linked rings. This data is used solely to provide and improve your gaming experience and is not associated with your personal identity, nor is it uploaded to any server or shared with any third parties.
•
Permissions: The App does not request any sensitive device permissions (e.g., camera, location, microphone, contacts, etc.).
2. Data Storage and Security
•
All game data generated by the App is stored exclusively on your device locally.
•
We do not transmit any of your information to external servers or cloud services.
•
As we do not collect personally identifiable information, there is no risk of user personal information being compromised due to data breaches.
3. Third-Party Services
The App does not integrate any third-party analytics, advertising, or social media services. Consequently, your data is not shared with any third-party service providers through this App.
4. Children's Privacy
This App is suitable for users of all ages, including children. Since we do not collect any personally identifiable information, we strictly adhere to the provisions of child online privacy protection laws (such as COPPA).
5. Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be communicated by updating the "Last Updated" date on this page. We encourage you to review this Privacy Policy periodically for any changes.
6. Contact Us
